1.  Implement interface commands to toggle autoadvance on and off.
    This can be a complementary type of bang suffix. So (1!), (2!), (3!) or
    (ht!), (md!), (xd!) will summon the getter for the attribute requested and
    thereafter autoadvance. Once in autoadvance entering lone (!) or
    bang-suffixed input like Duration(1, 8)! will enter input and terminate
    autoadvance.

